= SDL_QuitRequested =
Use this function to see whether an SLD_QUIT event is queued.


== Syntax ==
```c++
SDL_bool SDL_QuitRequested(void)
```

== Return Value ==
Returns SDL_TRUE if it is queued or SDL_FALSE otherwise.

